Resource Profile: BOADiagnosticReport

Official URL: https://profiles.ship.ume.de/StructureDefinition/boa-diagnostic-report Version: 0.1.1
Active as of 2024-10-02 Computable Name: BOADiagnosticReport

Segmentation and biomarker report generated with the Body and Organ Analysis (BOA) tool.

Usage:

  • This Resource Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide
